quran[37]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,"Hɑɑ miim"
  45,2,"Gafã sigbã yii Wẽnd nengẽ sẽn yaa wilb Naabã n yaa bʋʋd Mitã."
  45,3,"Ad be saasẽ la tẽngã zugu, yel-soalem-dãmbɑ ne sɩd-kõtba."
  45,4,"Lɑ yãmb naanegã pʋgẽ, la sẽn sãeegd sẽn yaa bõn-kẽndɩ fãa yaa yel-soalem ne bãng-n-wãaak rãmba."
  45,5,"Yʋngã ne wĩndgã yõs taabã, lɑ Wẽnd sẽn sikd rɩtlã n yit saasẽ wã n vɩɩmsd tẽngã ne-a a sẽn ki poorã, la sebgã kẽnesgã yaa yel-soalem ne yam rãmba."
  45,6,"Wã yaa Wẽnd aaya-rãmb tɩ D karemd-b fo zug ne sɩda; la yaa goam-bʋg la bãmb na n kõ sɩd ne Wẽnd ne A Aayayã poorẽ?"
  45,7,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-ned fãa sẽn yaa beegda."
  45,8,"Sẽn wʋmd Wẽnd Aayayã tɩ b karemd a zugu, rẽ poorẽ t'a kell n nadgd n waoogd a menga, tɩ yaa wala a pa wʋm-b ye, bɩ f noog a sũur ne namsg sẽn zabde."
  45,9,"La a sã n bãng bũmb Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã pʋgẽ, la a sẽn rɩkd-a ne yaalgo; bãmb rãmbã tara namsg sẽn faagde."
  45,10,"Gεhannem bee b poorẽ n gũud-bɑ. Bũmb ning bãmb sẽn paamã ka na n naf-b ba fʋɩ, b sẽn rɩk-b rãmb n maan lall-n-taas zẽng tɩ pa Wẽndã me, pa naf-d ba fʋɩ! La b tara namsg sẽn yaa zɩsgo."
  45,11,"Wã yaa kãndgre. La sẽn kɩfl-b ne b Soabã Aaya-rãmbã tara namsgo sẽn yaa naon-zabdga."
  45,12,"۞Wẽnd la Soab ning sẽn wõr mogrã n kõ yãmbã, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ koom kogendã na zoe a zug ne A sagelle, la y sẽn na paam A kũunã yĩnga, tɩ sand-sãnde y na pʋʋs barka."
  45,13,"La A wõr sẽn be saasẽ la sẽn be tẽng zug n kõ yãmba, fãa kɛp yaa sẽn yi A nengẽ; ad yel-soalem bee rẽ pʋgẽ ne tagsdba."
  45,14,"Yeel sẽn kõ-b sɩdã tɩ b bas tɩ loog sẽn pa tẽed-b Wẽnd rasem-rãmbã yĩnga, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ Wẽnd na rol nebã b sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  45,15,"Sẽn tʋm-a sõama, yaa a meng yĩnga, la sẽn wẽng-a me yaa a meng zugu; rẽ poorẽ yaa y Soabã nengẽ la b na n lebs-yã."
  45,16,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd kõo ɭsraεεl koambã gafã la bʋʋd la nabiyaamdem, la D rɩlg-b rɩ-yɩlma, la D yɩɩs-b bõn-naandsã zugu."
  45,17,"La D kõ-b vẽenem yellã pʋgẽ. La b pa yõs taaba rẽndame tɩ yaa bãngrã sẽn wa bãmb nengẽ poore, tɩ yaa kedgr bãmb ne taab sʋka. Ad fo Soabã n na n bʋ bãmb ne taab sʋk Dũni Yikr raare, b sẽn da yɩ n yõsd taab bũmb ning zugã."
  45,18,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd ning foom Sor zug sẽn yaa vẽeneg yellã pʋgẽ, bɩ f pʋg-a la f ra pʋg sẽn ka mi-bã yamleed ye."
  45,19,"Ad b pa tõe n naf foom ba fʋɩ n yɩɩd Wẽnd ye. Ad wẽgdbã yaa lall-n-taas ne taaba, la Wẽnd la wẽn-zoεtbã Lallda."
  45,20,"Wãnde yaa vẽenem ne nebã la kãndgr la yolsg ne bãng-n-wãak rãmba."
  45,21,"Bɩ sẽn tʋm-b wẽngã tẽedame tɩ Tõnd na n maan-b-la wala sẽn kõ-b sɩdã la b tʋm sõama wã, b vɩɩm wεεngẽ la b kũum wεεngẽ? Ad bãmb sẽn bʋʋdã yɩ wẽnga."
  45,22,"La Wẽnd naana saasã la tẽngã ne sɩda, la sẽn na rol yõor fãa gill a sẽn tʋme, tɩ bãmb yaa b sẽn pa wẽgd-b rãmb ye."
  45,23,"Fo pa yã sẽn rɩk-a a yamleoog tɩ yaa a soaba, tɩ Wẽnd menems-a bãngr zugu, n pag a tʋbã la a sũurã, n ning a ninẽ wã lutsi, yaa ãnd n na n pεεg-a Wẽnd poorẽ, Y pa na n tags n gese?"
  45,24,"La b yeele: ""vɩɩm kae tɩ sã n ka Dũni vɩɩmã ye, tɩ d kɩɩdẽ la d vɩɩmdẽ, la bũmb pa kʋʋd tõnd rẽnda zamaanã bala"". La bãmb ka tar bãngr buud ne rẽ ye, b pa yɩ, rẽndame tɩ yaa b sẽn tẽed bala."
  45,25,"La b sã n karemd b zugu Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã tɩ yaa vẽenese, b tikr ka yɩ rẽnda b sẽn yete: ""wa-y ne tõnd baaba-rãmbã tɩ y sã n yaa sɩd-rãmba""."
  45,26,"Yeel tɩ yaa Wẽnd n vɩɩmsd yãmba, rẽ poorẽ t'A kʋ yãmba, rẽ poorẽ t'A tigim-y n tʋg Dũni Yikr raare, sik ka a pʋgẽ ye, la ad nebã wʋsg pa mi ye."
  45,27,"La ad Wẽnd n so saasã la tẽngã naam, la Dũni wã Yikr raare, ra-kãng raare, zĩrimbe-nebã na n bõname."
  45,28,"La fo yãta zãma fãa t'a yĩga, zãma fãa b boond-a lame n tʋg a gafẽ: ""rũndã la b rond yãmb y sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã""."
  45,29,"Wã yaa Tõnd gaf sẽn gomd yãmb zug ne sɩda, ad Tõnd ra yɩɩme n gʋlsd yãmb sẽn da tʋmdã."
  45,30,"La sã n yaa sẽn kõ-b sɩdã la b tʋm sõama wã, b Soabã kẽesd-b-la A yolsgã pʋgẽ, rẽ la pʋɩɩr sẽn yaa vẽenega."
  45,31,"La sã n yaa sẽn kɩfl-bã (Wẽnd yet-b lame): ""rẽ yĩngã Mam Aaya-rãmbã, b ra pa yɩ n karemd-b yãmb zugu, tɩ yãmb waoog y mense, la y ra yɩ n yaa nin-wẽnse?""."
  45,32,"La b sã n yeel tɩ Wẽnd pʋlengã yaa sɩda, la Dũni Yikrã sik ka a pʋgẽ, yãmb yetame: ""tõnd pa mi Dũni Yirk ye, tõnd pa tẽed rẽndame tɩ yaa sãmbs bala, la tõnd pa yɩ n yaa bãng-n-wãag rãmb ye""."
  45,33,"Tɩ bãmb sẽn tʋmã wẽng puk ne bãmba, tɩ gũbg bãmb bũmb ning bãmb sẽn da yɩ n yaandẽ wã."
  45,34,"Tɩ b yeele: ""rũndã D yĩmda yãmb yell wala yãmb sẽn yĩm y ra-kãngã segbã, la y gãag zĩig yaa Bugmẽ, y pa tar sõngd buudu""."
  45,35,"Yaa woto tɩ bala yãmb rɩka Wẽnd Aaya-rãmbã ne yaalgo, tɩ Dũni vɩɩmã belg yãmba, rẽnd rũndã b pa na n yiis yãmb a pʋgẽ ye, b pa na n leb yaaf-b ye."
  45,36,"Rẽnd Pẽgr tiugung be ne Wẽnde, saas la tẽng Naabã, bõn-naands Naabã."
  45,37,"La Yẽ n so waoog-m-menga, saasẽ la tẽnga, la Yẽ la ɑ Wind n yaa bʋʋd Mita."
